{
  "title": "Google admin console",
  "slug": "google-admin-console",
  "categorySlug": "data-sources",
  "html": "<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell \" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-1 dnd-section kb-article-row-0-padding\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell dnd-column\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-2 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-2\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-3 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h1 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">Google admin console</h1>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-4 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h2 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">A simple step-by-step guide of how to set up permissions for your Google accounts. </h2>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-5 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_richtext_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_richtext_field\"><div class=\"hs-embed-wrapper\" data-service=\"share.synthesia\"><div class=\"hs-embed-content-wrapper\"><div style=\"position: relative; overflow: hidden; aspect-ratio: 1920/1080\"><iframe src=\"https://share.synthesia.io/embeds/videos/d8057d92-e0c3-4d48-893b-ae8fe2711792\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Synthesia video player - Data &amp; More - Gmail Integration Setup Guide (Google Cloud Service Account)\" allowfullscreen=\"\" allow=\"encrypted-media; fullscreen; microphone; screen-wake-lock;\" style=\"position: absolute; width: 100%; height: 100%; top: 0; left: 0; border: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; overflow:hidden;\"></iframe></div></div></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>First, you need to visit <a href=\"https://console.cloud.google.com/\">https://console.cloud.google.com/</a> and login (Note: the account needs to have admin rights).&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"hs-callout-type-warning\" data-hs-callout-type=\"warning\">\n<p><strong>When your are done sennd us your JSON file </strong>created in this process so we can start with scanning and cleaning up your data! <strong>AND&nbsp; the your D&amp;M contact what&nbsp; global admin users that was used to create the JSON<br><br>We need BOTH the JSON and the the name of the globals admin email in order to procee.</strong></p>\n</div>\n\n<p>1. When you log in, the page should look like on the screenshot below. First step is to create a project and to do that, click on the button marked red on the same screenshot.</p>\n<br>\n<p><img alt=\"Screenshot 2025-05-23 at 10.41.26\" class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"235\" style=\"width: 624px; height: auto;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-05-23%20at%2010.41.26.png?width=624&amp;height=235&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-05-23%20at%2010.41.26.png\" width=\"624\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-05-23%20at%2010.41.26.png?width=312&amp;height=118&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-05-23%20at%2010.41.26.png 312w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-05-23%20at%2010.41.26.png?width=624&amp;height=235&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-05-23%20at%2010.41.26.png 624w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-05-23%20at%2010.41.26.png?width=936&amp;height=353&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-05-23%20at%2010.41.26.png 936w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-05-23%20at%2010.41.26.png?width=1248&amp;height=470&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-05-23%20at%2010.41.26.png 1248w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-05-23%20at%2010.41.26.png?width=1560&amp;height=588&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-05-23%20at%2010.41.26.png 1560w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-05-23%20at%2010.41.26.png?width=1872&amp;height=705&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-05-23%20at%2010.41.26.png 1872w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 624px) 100vw, 624px\"></p>\n<br>\n<p>2. New page should open where button “New project” needs to be visible and selected.</p>\n<br>\n<p><img alt=\"Screenshot 2025-05-23 at 10.42.31\" class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"481\" style=\"width: 624px; height: auto;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-05-23%20at%2010.42.31.png?width=624&amp;height=481&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-05-23%20at%2010.42.31.png\" width=\"624\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-05-23%20at%2010.42.31.png?width=312&amp;height=241&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-05-23%20at%2010.42.31.png 312w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-05-23%20at%2010.42.31.png?width=624&amp;height=481&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-05-23%20at%2010.42.31.png 624w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-05-23%20at%2010.42.31.png?width=936&amp;height=722&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-05-23%20at%2010.42.31.png 936w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-05-23%20at%2010.42.31.png?width=1248&amp;height=962&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-05-23%20at%2010.42.31.png 1248w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-05-23%20at%2010.42.31.png?width=1560&amp;height=1203&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-05-23%20at%2010.42.31.png 1560w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-05-23%20at%2010.42.31.png?width=1872&amp;height=1443&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-05-23%20at%2010.42.31.png 1872w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 624px) 100vw, 624px\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>3. To create a new project, all you need to do is to write a name of it (with no spaces) and click on <em>Create</em> button.</p>\n<br>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"361\" style=\"width: 624px; height: auto;\" src=\"https://lh7-qw.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXfZwGfJyglQ0-Av8C2Ay7Hr-JYTiri265p3-dszY4fg5_lFlgj1_c_gMCtsBXTYejk-4JVhYfgQPMxe52rN-6ZPiqVDRM0dZoFG3AHk6bHMUkJF3HQYDeowZl4jis5_9z2dURhB?key=yYjcS0N9NRxGK7etRfXkpw\" width=\"624\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p>4. After you created a project, your page should look like on the screenshot below. Just make sure that your new project is selected. It's easy to check it - the name of it should be visible on the button marked with red box on the same screenshot.</p>\n<br>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"208\" style=\"width: 624px; height: auto;\" src=\"https://lh7-qw.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXfE0wm6RICNnBrs5Ni81MRG-pTTY1Kjg5CLqdq05Pvb0HGhgvKOlNhugpePxdfzQ306DfjM2ti4gVpZoabyxNncII4Kgg5JfqjPJSfeVoUZ0MuO1neBA_cWTl1iSOTnwJ0cE4tz?key=yYjcS0N9NRxGK7etRfXkpw\" width=\"624\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<br>\n<p>5. Once you have your project created and opened, click on the menu on the left and select <em>APIs&nbsp; &amp; Services &gt; Library</em></p>\n<br>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"263\" style=\"width: 624px; height: auto;\" src=\"https://lh7-qw.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXfz8fWHwxd-sUMFDRbf3XjTw15Pjnr_FLA4HZyvL0PIFk-UrmxMuf4FEqWUZFsZKtEvASSJxJ1eq0WdWcnerIywXLSIPFg9UyZO-fWN780P97c9YfQWxHbmOwvXOnrR43gSX6ygJw?key=yYjcS0N9NRxGK7etRfXkpw\" width=\"624\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<br>\n<p>6. After Library is opened, type in \"Gmail API\" in the search bar and click on the first result:</p>\n<br><br>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"231\" style=\"width: 624px; height: auto;\" src=\"https://lh7-qw.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXcCaJ9fVnRbSE4kmDeqygRO4UvUOelP1k6mzqaKtVui-bUeUZL-uvIqwwtYfWDygjf1lfff_4DNsLZo14Gvr8UQLrtrmUmQAnenueuPCqANE6KvOk51ReI9ESp1k4O8hkSlats1?key=yYjcS0N9NRxGK7etRfXkpw\" width=\"624\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>7. Product details should be opened and all you need to do there is click on <em>Enable</em> button:</p>\n<br>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"336\" style=\"width: 624px; height: auto;\" src=\"https://lh7-qw.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXeTSa1K25LZRSrStX8zhxqStKgacJieQy4Sbr--crs5Nw9rhEyz01gpJLcSsuIWN1A1cMQc0SVaMcOEFm-veV_ExczYguMIwMF4P--vQLN8No4c0n18MTz-apTc6TWI4ubwpWvbMQ?key=yYjcS0N9NRxGK7etRfXkpw\" width=\"624\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<br>\n<p>8. After you enable it, your page should look like the one on the screenshot below. From there, click on <em>Credentials &gt; Create credentials &gt; OUauth client ID:</em></p>\n<p><img alt=\"Screenshot 2025-07-10 at 13.40.01\" class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"208\" style=\"height: auto; width: 670px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.40.01.png?width=670&amp;height=208&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.40.01.png\" width=\"670\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.40.01.png?width=335&amp;height=104&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.40.01.png 335w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.40.01.png?width=670&amp;height=208&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.40.01.png 670w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.40.01.png?width=1005&amp;height=312&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.40.01.png 1005w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.40.01.png?width=1340&amp;height=416&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.40.01.png 1340w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.40.01.png?width=1675&amp;height=520&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.40.01.png 1675w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.40.01.png?width=2010&amp;height=624&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.40.01.png 2010w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 670px) 100vw, 670px\"></p>\n<p>9.<em>&nbsp;</em>Application type should be \"Web application\":</p>\n<p><em><img alt=\"Screenshot 2025-07-10 at 13.41.14\" class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"326\" style=\"height: auto; width: 670px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.41.14.png?width=670&amp;height=326&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.41.14.png\" width=\"670\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.41.14.png?width=335&amp;height=163&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.41.14.png 335w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.41.14.png?width=670&amp;height=326&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.41.14.png 670w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.41.14.png?width=1005&amp;height=489&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.41.14.png 1005w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.41.14.png?width=1340&amp;height=652&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.41.14.png 1340w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.41.14.png?width=1675&amp;height=815&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.41.14.png 1675w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.41.14.png?width=2010&amp;height=978&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.41.14.png 2010w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 670px) 100vw, 670px\"></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>10. Give a name for your OAuth client ID. It's only used to identify the client in the console and it will not be showed to end users. When you entered the name, click on <em>Add URL</em> under \"Authorized redirect URLs\":</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Screenshot 2025-07-10 at 13.42.13\" class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"415\" style=\"height: auto; width: 670px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.42.13.png?width=670&amp;height=415&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.42.13.png\" width=\"670\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.42.13.png?width=335&amp;height=208&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.42.13.png 335w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.42.13.png?width=670&amp;height=415&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.42.13.png 670w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.42.13.png?width=1005&amp;height=623&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.42.13.png 1005w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.42.13.png?width=1340&amp;height=830&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.42.13.png 1340w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.42.13.png?width=1675&amp;height=1038&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.42.13.png 1675w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.42.13.png?width=2010&amp;height=1245&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.42.13.png 2010w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 670px) 100vw, 670px\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>11. Enter redirect URLs</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\"the primary server domain\" + \"<em>/api/auth/google/login/callback</em>\"</li>\n<li>\n<p>So if your server domain is:&nbsp;<em>https://dev.gdpr.dataandmore.com</em>&nbsp;then redirect URL should be:</p>\n<p><em>https://dev.gdpr.dataandmore.com<strong>/api/auth/google/login/callback</strong></em></p>\n</li>\n<li><em><strong>And a universal return URL for PoC</strong></em><br>https://signup.dataandmore.com/api/authorize_redirect_google</li>\n</ul>\n<p>After that, click on <em>Create.</em></p>\n<p><img alt=\"Screenshot 2025-07-10 at 13.51.06\" class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"444\" style=\"height: auto; width: 670px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.51.06.png?width=670&amp;height=444&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.51.06.png\" width=\"670\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.51.06.png?width=335&amp;height=222&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.51.06.png 335w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.51.06.png?width=670&amp;height=444&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.51.06.png 670w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.51.06.png?width=1005&amp;height=666&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.51.06.png 1005w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.51.06.png?width=1340&amp;height=888&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.51.06.png 1340w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.51.06.png?width=1675&amp;height=1110&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.51.06.png 1675w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.51.06.png?width=2010&amp;height=1332&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.51.06.png 2010w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 670px) 100vw, 670px\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>12. New pop up window will appear where you have to copy <strong>Client ID</strong> and <strong>Client secret</strong> before clicking on <em>OK</em>. That is the data that needs to be sent to us.</p>\n<p><em><img alt=\"Screenshot 2025-07-10 at 13.52.16\" class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"771\" style=\"height: auto; width: 670px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.52.16.png?width=670&amp;height=771&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.52.16.png\" width=\"670\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.52.16.png?width=335&amp;height=386&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.52.16.png 335w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.52.16.png?width=670&amp;height=771&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.52.16.png 670w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.52.16.png?width=1005&amp;height=1157&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.52.16.png 1005w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.52.16.png?width=1340&amp;height=1542&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.52.16.png 1340w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.52.16.png?width=1675&amp;height=1928&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.52.16.png 1675w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.52.16.png?width=2010&amp;height=2313&amp;name=Screenshot%202025-07-10%20at%2013.52.16.png 2010w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 670px) 100vw, 670px\"></em></p>\n<p>13. Now, we need to add a service account. To do that, go to<em> Credentials &gt; Manage service accounts</em>:</p>\n<br>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"235\" style=\"width: 624px; height: auto;\" src=\"https://lh7-qw.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXf8TTUGHKIB9iMdxT0eC3yZsj74hSCuD3L06IyTN56JhpipImukKziVs4RoIxsE01oSZHWto9iG4JxPZizCY2plL1iDrn_OgtDVJLjrRAmxX6K1qYwBEzSuSiGPpf2b3Tgv7MRzIw?key=yYjcS0N9NRxGK7etRfXkpw\" width=\"624\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>14. When on service accounts page, click on <em>Create service account</em> (marked with red on screenshot below):</p>\n<br>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"225\" style=\"width: 624px; height: auto;\" src=\"https://lh7-qw.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXf8NeI1FQsy-4H2ZdnMugrM7Fr3HkKOjeaienijJAbU5hSOhAonUIK7eUqaVkWBNgSmkTMllWdChgA4i3Htnby3LuqFYR1lpraEPABeFJo_IUCJ1HLhJ9iUZk2xLt6I0wIU1tRJ8g?key=yYjcS0N9NRxGK7etRfXkpw\" width=\"624\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<br>\n<p>15. The page like on screenshot below should be visible now. Enter your service account name (whatever you prefer), copy the email address that is been created because you’ll need it later, and click on <em>Done</em>.</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"393\" style=\"width: 624px; height: auto;\" src=\"https://lh7-qw.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXdq5yUhZpTIOL0ZZAqZ839geKLg-RJ4MhnqCrto7FR0q8Z3B31ywg5OlAUpd2U5s3En7pkT30q4cYSgBWn8wE2qmzc4uXjCc9vBfgp8mrffNTEdg_b_Mb-_k1mCUXD3NwEli5ehcQ?key=yYjcS0N9NRxGK7etRfXkpw\" width=\"624\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>16. Now your service account is visible in the table. To proceed, click on the email (marked with red box on screenshot below):</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"299\" style=\"width: 624px; height: auto;\" src=\"https://lh7-qw.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXeGOEoo6dJSvrUGA8TuOOJgnNi3IgwW6FqBYAXAn_O8aHu1DJpSFohFesyImu2ZAHZlJUiV16qEAwu8bBb_8RuLLC4QVQs6ziLiqB7ah-uNN16xY2LQplOoxmJo8kfjxJifTYLM?key=yYjcS0N9NRxGK7etRfXkpw\" width=\"624\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<br><br>\n<p>17. From there, open the tab <em>Keys</em> and go to <em>Add key &gt; Create new key</em>:</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"251\" style=\"width: 624px; height: auto;\" src=\"https://lh7-qw.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXd5Kk-fsYwz3clPliX5ywc73bGXPnD5G_h1jpX9LXXDXUNWWGXIeMircewvCNSTHDWmpWhsb8g6dMdkLc_GyAXCNLLioPkI2r_lD_jzAOVrRFocdrUHdUqYWDSX-PC0w7mQW61Ihg?key=yYjcS0N9NRxGK7etRfXkpw\" width=\"624\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<br>\n<p>18. Default selection will be JSON file and it needs to stay like that. Click on <em>Create</em>. The JSON file will be downloaded and we are going to use it for App registration on our Toolbox.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"372\" style=\"width: 624px; height: auto;\" src=\"https://lh7-qw.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXcD5YV1sXRPCr0W4_wFJ2GUco8-wcifX2rHLuY0ZWqUV6iX__MfeNWt8BBXoDYcekCprnBgM3mn6AZnuHxHduEuyg9eW7Egika0yZavsFfvOdo0GUh9tOM84COmvKCsAAWYKCqW?key=yYjcS0N9NRxGK7etRfXkpw\" width=\"624\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>19. After your key is created, you need to go to <em>Details</em> tab, scroll a bit down and copy the Client ID because you’ll need it later. After that, click on <em>View Google Workspace Admin Console</em>.</p>\n<br>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"313\" style=\"width: 624px; height: auto;\" src=\"https://lh7-qw.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXfjF-JsZpcCUFTQvTp0_2Eyhlx1ZTyNYtCUXL9Efe3Ry074LB9Qe32lxE4bS-aBTVu5b_rUrwjHEgZ2st9l26T8Aw4osi5sjbAuDbGH3yUHS1jEuryJxXSh7EHFeD8lLJs-KeHjYg?key=yYjcS0N9NRxGK7etRfXkpw\" width=\"624\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<br>\n<p>20. In your Admin console go to the side menu and click on <em>Security &gt; Access and data control &gt; API controls</em>. Scroll a bit down until you see <em>Manage domain wide delegation</em> and click on it.</p>\n<br><br><br>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"305\" style=\"width: 624px; height: auto;\" src=\"https://lh7-qw.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXcq4dQZp30NiguSMpQ9UIDLsw9EeTZdrRNaVccFRQ8el_tKr9t2dLZqRo0RoAmpYbEVeVQU4i-Bu8GeO9c1_4VtyaAQ2-LEn01c4kCNGSsEa5hEp3OCHVmU2C3rDutuC8i99nR6MQ?key=yYjcS0N9NRxGK7etRfXkpw\" width=\"624\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<br>\n<p>21. Click on <em>Add new</em>:</p>\n<br>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"155\" style=\"width: 624px; height: auto;\" src=\"https://lh7-qw.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXdHF3V6w4oMYwSq9T_aBrvr0mH0qiJHM3f3rgn0vk-EbZCrYPkNa98d15v8X_Y5ZuZaRD4tBxbPCUlPsCVuVp7Rkdv_HokTB0SfHGjrEhjfzcRmG_lTo9GS2_D7XqOEpxLH9n-7gg?key=yYjcS0N9NRxGK7etRfXkpw\" width=\"624\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<br>\n<p>17. New pop up window should be opened. Here you can enter Client ID that you copied earlier and these four links that are actually permissions (you can enter all four links in the same text input but they need to be separated with a comma or you can enter them separately):</p>\n<br>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.googleapis.com/auth/gmail.readonly\">https://www.googleapis.com/auth/gmail.readonly</a></p>\n<br>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.googleapis.com/auth/admin.directory.user.readonly\">https://www.googleapis.com/auth/admin.directory.user.readonly</a></p>\n<br>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.googleapis.com/auth/gmail.labels\">https://www.googleapis.com/auth/gmail.labels</a></p>\n<br>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.googleapis.com/auth/gmail.modify\">https://www.googleapis.com/auth/gmail.modify</a></p>\n<br><br>\n<p>After you entered all necessary information, click on <em>Authorize</em>:</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"561\" style=\"width: 624px; height: auto;\" src=\"https://lh7-qw.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXdj9Ihl8KIHi16RAnaHnWz2Glnff3Xe96pNu0IpdAcVW4CLhjCx6PUVA8rw-LUZF1OSbsNiYADOQ0jGQ6ljTGDR0Tz0ab7vHzi_PTYyjcc7HPcII2E69qEZW2TyZshPtJCdn1SozA?key=yYjcS0N9NRxGK7etRfXkpw\" width=\"624\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<br>\n<p>22. Your newly created API client should be visible in the table like on screenshot below:</p>\n<br>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"135\" style=\"width: 624px; height: auto;\" src=\"https://lh7-qw.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXdXZudzbnpRUITtbMnbTZ8-aCnzGcpVwA3IgiOTbe3syJmCN4EfC60kSnC-AJV_towryGsEEWzFhWBJpdIVvLB7_t9Q90v77QKsFLwkQYmGwIXRufzzXaqJZq8XjdVf1dsCHdRmrA?key=yYjcS0N9NRxGK7etRfXkpw\" width=\"624\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<br><br>\n<p>And that’s it! Whenever you are ready, <strong>send us your JSON file </strong>created in this process so we can start with scanning and cleaning up your data! <strong>AND the global admin email that was used to create the JSON</strong></p></div>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div>\n</div>",
  "sourceUrl": "https://support.dataandmore.com/en/knowledge/google-admin-console"
}